T1  - Influence Sources of Project and Functional Managers in Matrix Organizations
AU  - Dunne, Edward J.
AU  - Stahl, Michael J.
AU  - Melhart, Leonard J.
Y1  - 1978/03/01
PY  - 1978
DA  - 1978/03/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/255670
